Subject: drm/radeon: Use RMW accessors for changing LNKCTL2
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 756762aeb11ae1befbbcb7a04cf213a0a67c2646
